# Academy Content Machine — API keys (already in Nelson's ~/.zshrc shell).
# Only needed if you run the machine where the shell vars aren't loaded.
# Copy to ".env" and `source .env` (or use a dotenv loader) before running.

GOOGLE_API_KEY=        # Nano Banana 2 / Gemini image  (gemini-3.1-flash-image)
OPENAI_API_KEY=        # ChatGPT image  (gpt-image-1 / gpt-image-2 edits)

# Optional model overrides:
# GEN_MODEL_GEMINI=gemini-3.1-flash-image
# GEN_MODEL_OPENAI=gpt-image-1
# GEN_MODEL_OPENAI_EDIT=gpt-image-2
